            <title><![CDATA[中国大陆对台驻美代表萧美琴实施进一步制裁]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/07/E890A7E7BE8EE790B4.jpg?VersionId=VdLOeOfrzCWtuTbqQfL9k.rfdDuBMv3i&amp;itok=xxeJuAqI" title="中国大陆星期五（4月7日）宣布，对台湾驻美代表萧美琴实施进一步制裁。（互联网）" alt="中国大陆星期五（4月7日）宣布，对台湾驻美代表萧美琴实施进一步制裁。（互联网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/07/E890A7E7BE8EE790B4.jpg?VersionId=VdLOeOfrzCWtuTbqQfL9k.rfdDuBMv3i&amp;itok=xxeJuAqI" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
